{"type":null,"faqId":43855,"title":"华为手机如何跟B2建立连接？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n.s2{color:black;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0006944in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span class=\"s2\">首次配对连接：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">手环开机之后，界面左上角蓝牙图条闪烁，表明可以进行配对连接</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">打开手机蓝牙，在蓝牙列表中点击“HUAWEI B2-XXX”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2. 第二次配对连接：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1）手机与手环解除配对后，想要再次配对连接，需长按手环侧键3s，点击屏幕上的蓝牙图标</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=154000\" style=\"width:0.3236111in;height:0.45625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s2\"> ，图标闪烁表示进入配对模式，打开手机蓝牙，在蓝牙列表中点击“HUAWEI B2-XXX”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2）手环可以同时连接两部手机。连接第二个手机时，长按手环侧键3s，点击屏幕上的蓝牙图标</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=154001\" style=\"width:0.3236111in;height:0.45625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s2\"> ，图标闪烁表示进入配对模式，然后再点击第二个手机蓝牙列表中的“HUAWEI B2-XXX”即可连接。（备注：此时手环会和第一个连接的手机蓝牙断连，点击第一个手机的蓝牙配对列表中的“HUAWEI B2-XXX”后，手环上蓝牙图标右下角出现数字2时说明手环和两个手机连接成功）</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3）蓝牙连接上之后，打开“华为穿戴”APP，通过引导界面进入主界面，在主界面下拉第一次同步数据。显示同步成功后，手环的时间和各项信息已经初始化，您就可以正常使用手环了。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9356","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399558000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":10,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"B,连接,蓝牙","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}